summary: Master student Financial Economics at Erasmus university, concluding a long academic process that took me from vmbo all the way to a masters degree at university. Engaged student with extensive English, French and Russian Language skills, partly due to having lived in The Russian Federation, France and The Balkans. I have experience in programming, data science and professional experience in the banking industry.
